lead_paragraph: Mississippi Valley State was hanging fairly close with nationally ranked Michigan State earlier this year before Spartans' guard Miles Bridges took a pass, sprinted down the lane and threw down a vicious one-handed dunk over Jamal Watson.

headline.print_headline: Lower-Level Division I Teams Embrace, Enjoy Epic Road Trips
